Topic: Install GNU Radio and the SDR block module for accessing the Usb SDR dongle
Device: ASUS Tinker Board (2017)
OS: 20171115-tinker-board-linaro-stretch-alip-v2.0.4

# Install GNU Radio:
sudo apt-get install gnuradio
sudo apt-get install gnuradio-dev

# Install SDR Module for GNU Radio:
sudo apt-get install gr-osmosdr

# Update the system’s list of installed code libraries:
sudo ldconfig

# Reboot the Tinker Board:
sudo reboot

# Now GNU Radio should be available as “GRC” at:
Desktop > Home Icon > Programming > GRC 

# In the GNU Radio application the SDR block is found in the modules menu under: 
(no module specified) > Sources > RTL-SDR Source
